 The accident that involved 17 vehicles occurred at the N4/N12 split due to heavy mist on the roads .    TRAC has confirmed that the N12 split remains closed due to heavy mist. The Traffic Department closed the N12 at the Ogies intersection which resulted in the closure at the split.
Motorists are advised to use the R555 between Ogies and eMalahleni as an alternative route and to proceed with caution.        Middelburg police officer arrested during Hawks operation Botshabelo’s last song Five busted for dagga Nabbed cops granted bail  • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za